Root `.pre-commit-config.yaml` is a **symlink** to `configs/v4/.pre-commit-config.yaml`. Edit hook versions and repos under `configs/v4/` only.

CI enforces: `cmp -s configs/v4/.pre-commit-config.yaml .pre-commit-config.yaml`.

See **AGENTS.md** for the full hook list and sweep command.
